  "text": "A complementary line of algorithms starts with [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , who consider certain separability assumptions on the input data to circumvent NP-Hardness of the basic LDA model. These works have shown performance competitive to Gibbs sampling in some scenarios while also featuring theoretical guarantees. Other recent viewpoints on LDA are offered by [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
